Imaobong Nse Uko (amuru na ọnwa 20 February na afọ 2004) bu onye egwuregwu Naijiria
Ọ gbara ọsọ na mmemme ịgbagharị 4 × 400 agwakọtara na asọmpi Olimpik Summer 2020
Onye dị afọ 17 meriri ihe nrite ọla edo n'elu 400 mita na asọmpi 2021 World Under 20
Uko gụsịrị akwụkwọ sekọndrị na Apostolic Church Secondary School, Ikot Oku Nsit
Ọ bụ onye mmeri 400m Youth na Akwa Ibom Youth Sports Festival na 2018
Ọ gụchara n'ọkwa nke abụọ na nzukọ n'afọ gara aga
Mgbe ọ dị afọ 14, ọ ghọrọ onye mmeri Nigeria National Sports Festival (NSF) na mita 400, na-emeri aha ya na nke kacha mma nke 52.36
Ọ kpataara iwe nke tụrụ ndị ntaakụkọ na ndị ọrụ ọchịchị anya ka ọ na-akụ ndị egwuregwu toro eto na ndị nwere ahụmahụ ka ha were ọkwa
Yinka Ajayi nọ n'ọkwa dị egwu n'afọ ahụ, na-eme asọmpi Commonwealth wee bụrụ onye mmeri n'asọmpị Bronze nke Africa na 400m, ya mere a tụrụ anya na ọ ga-abụ ọkwa
Otú ọ dị, onye meriri ihe nrite Bronze Africa, Ajayi, kwesịrị ịnọ n'ọnọdụ nke abụọ n'azụ nwata ahụ
Oge a bụ ebe Uko kwuputara onwe ya nye ndị Naijiria ndị ọzọ ka ha na-ele anya maka ọdịnihu
Ka emechara mmemme ahụ, gọọmentị Akwa Ibom kwụrụ ya na onye nkuzi ya ụgwọ ọrụ
Ọ bụkwa onye mmeri nke 2019 Nigerian U 18 na mita 400
Ọ gbachitere aha NSF ya nke ọma na 2021
N'ime emume egwuregwu mba Edo 2020 nke emere na 2021 ka ebigharịrị ha n'ihi ọrịa COVID-19, ọ gbara afọ 52 na nke mbụ
Ọ meriri Patience Okon George n'oge ahụ iji nweta aha ya na nke kacha mma nke 51.70s
Ọ kwadokwara Team Akwa Ibom ka ọ nweta mmeri n'asọmpị 4x400m nke ụmụ nwanyị
Ihe omume ya na ememme ahụ mere ka a họrọ ya n'ime ndị otu Naijiria e zigara ịzụ ọzụzụ na United States tupu asọmpi Tokyo Olympic
Ọ debere nke atọ na asọmpi egwuregwu egwuregwu Naịjirịa na 2021 Olympic n'azụ George na Knowledge Omovoh nke nyere aka nweta ọnọdụ ya na ndị otu egwuregwu Olympic
N'oge asọmpi World U20, ọ gbara ụkwụ nke abụọ nke agba agba agba agba agba agba agba agba 4x400
Ndị otu Naijiria mebere Johnson Chidera Nnamani, Uko, Opeyemi Deborah Oke na Bamidele Ajayi meriri emume a na asọmpi asọmpi n'oge 3:19.70
